subSubSection.paragraph:
Type material. Holotype (formerly paratype of
Foza ambohitra
): Madagascar : adult ♂ ( CW 43.0, CL 31.6, CH 17.7, FW 11.6 mm ), Toamasina Province, Analanjirofo Region, Akirindro Mountain, 7.6 km NNW of Ambinantelo, ( 15.2883°S , 49.5483°E ) 600 m ASL , coll. P. Naskrecki, 17–21 March 2003 (NMU PN 17– 21.3.2003 ) (GenBank MT749730 ).

Medium-sized species, the only known specimen is an adult male (CW 
43 mm
).
